WEBVTT

00:12:59.707 --> 00:13:03.903
You know, suddenly there was this
animated conversation between us,

00:13:03.927 --> 00:13:06.053
there was this wonderful connection.

00:13:06.077 --> 00:13:10.260
AdG: But sometimes, genuine enthusiasm
just doesn't get reciprocated.

00:13:10.641 --> 00:13:14.148
JL: I remember working
on "3rd Rock from the Sun."

00:13:14.172 --> 00:13:18.874
We had a guest actor
who was famously difficult to work with.

00:13:19.284 --> 00:13:24.188
A big, big star, but temper tantrums
and egotistical behavior.

00:13:24.993 --> 00:13:28.393
And sure enough, it was impossible.

00:13:28.841 --> 00:13:33.474
I did everything I could
to accommodate this person --